        Essential PivotGrid for WPF
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph  FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14">
        PivotGrid for WPF Edition is a powerful cell-oriented extensible grid control. It simulates the pivot table feature of Excel. The pivot grid, as the name implies, pivots data through the drag-and-drop operation, to organize the data in a cross-tabulated form. The major advantage with pivot grid is that you can extract the desired information from a large list within seconds. Along with presenting the data, it also enables you to summarize and group data. It finds its main application in the financial domain, where it is used to organize and analyze business data.
    </Paragraph>

